{"tid":2440215,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"三十秒科學–自割","createTime":"2021-03-09T21:12:47.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-10T17:59:20.000Z","uid":38861,"like":99,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"b6ba80d89e703939ee30f5ee6e7b94c255c8cd2c","tid":2440215,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T21:12:47.000Z","msg":"自割 (Autotomy)是一種動物求生的本能，其中的例子包括壁虎斷尾，螃蟹斷臂等等。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hx2NZ0c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fhx2NZ0c.jpg&h=a8826157&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n過一段時間後，器官便會再生回復至原來的樣貌，其體積有機會比原來的更為細少。<br />\n<br />\n（圖2）有科學家嘗試用尼龍蠅綁住海蛞蝓(Sea Slug)的頸部，發現牠們有能力進行自割，頭身分離。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BBrbHdA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBBrbHdA.png&h=fc39ce67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有情況甚至是頭部與心臟、大腸、性器官等分離。而其脫離的頭部則吃著海藻維生。<br />\n<br />\n7日後，頭部發展出心臟等器官。約20日後，所有器官亦能順利發展成為原狀，又一條好漢。<br />\n<br />\n至於被遺棄的身體，則隨著時間變得暗淡及萎縮，沒能長出頭部。<br />\n<br />\n（圖3）自然情況下，當海蛞蝓遭受到寄生蟲入侵時，進行自割並頭身分離的情況亦會發生。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5u6fpr4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5u6fpr4.png&h=ca63a55b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n鑑於這情況的發生，有理由可相信海蛞蝓進行自割是天生用來對抗外敵入侵的手段。<br />\n<br />\n此地不宜久留之時，若有逃生門手段可走，自然界的生物自當會不惜一切進行逃離。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果想我快啲出文的話，請入去Penana網站科普專欄&ndash;薯不揀單俾一個like以及Bookmark，這對我非常之重要。<br />\n<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fstory%2F66244%2F%25E7%25A7%2591%25E6%2599%25AE%25E5%25B0%2588%25E6%25AC%2584-%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%258F%2580%25E5%2596%25AE%2Ftoc&d=QSug7dhZHD7voFbR5lwple4Wvb5rKEvwepesSl%2FR16E%3D&h=a971aeb4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc</a><br />\n<br />\n同時亦可以在Penana網站裡按「買一嚿/半嚿薯仔」，以課金的方式推動我繼續搜羅資料寫文，多謝。<br />\n<br />\nLink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fuser%2F27349%2F%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25BB%2594%25E8%2581%259E%25E8%258C%25B1%25E8%258E%2589%2Fportfolio&d=QSug7dhZHD7voFbR5lwple4Wvb5rKEvwepesSl%2FR16E%3D&h=ed75efcd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n除非Facebook及IG重開侵侵的account，否則我的IG將不會再作更新，只會寄居本土LIHKG及Penana。<br />\n<br />\nRef1:<a href=\"https://www.cell.com/current-biology/fulltext/S0960-9822\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cell.com%2Fcurrent-biology%2Ffulltext%2FS0960-9822&d=QSug7dhZHD7voFbR5lwple4Wvb5rKEvwepesSl%2FR16E%3D&h=0b8e24f1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cell.com/current-biology/fulltext/S0960-9822</a>(21)00047-6"},{"pid":"a9290af4b3d8ad2b7ebe9731f8c9e8db06477219","tid":2440215,"uid":255980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T21:13:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01171b479eeabeff8580dbca0d6ffca53ae59a70","tid":2440215,"uid":172172,"like":46,"dislike":0,"score":46,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T21:14:13.000Z","msg":"以為割J"},{"pid":"c9ff7de4f794938f0ecfbe88199a1819597b9b82","tid":2440215,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"01171b479eeabeff8580dbca0d6ffca53ae59a70","tid":2440215,"uid":172172,"like":46,"dislike":0,"score":46,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T21:14:13.000Z","msg":"以為割J"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T21:16:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84ab29b699996a8d6651ca719151ae50ff8dc14d","tid":2440215,"uid":246336,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"ci